  "detailed_description": "Gear up, confront your demons, and brace yourself for a descent into the abyss. In \"Pillars of Sorrow,\" the battle is not just against enemies on the screen but against the shadows that lurk within yourself. Your journey awaits, brave soul.<br><br>Step into the chilling abyss of the Halloween update where the ghosts of the past rise from the shadows, interwining with the malevolent creatures that haunt the very essence of Halloween itself.<br><br>Engage in a fierce battle against the shadows within as you traverse the haunting landscapes of three (+ one) main zones.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872920/extras/9911187aa7352dcc11e0815cd227bc0e.poster.avif?t=1723036400\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872920/extras/9911187aa7352dcc11e0815cd227bc0e.webm?t=1723036400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872920/extras/9911187aa7352dcc11e0815cd227bc0e.mp4?t=1723036400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Elevate your abilities to unlock mighty skills, transforming yourself into an unstoppable force.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872920/extras/533c46d3bbff228009b505945efa0d2a.poster.avif?t=1723036400\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872920/extras/533c46d3bbff228009b505945efa0d2a.webm?t=1723036400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872920/extras/533c46d3bbff228009b505945efa0d2a.mp4?t=1723036400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Embark on a thrilling hunt to gather cute